summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 9481, entitled "An Ordinance providing for the improvement of University Street, in the City of Seattle, from Second Avenue to Third Avenue, by planking the same, under Resolution No. 520, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Immediate Payment", under the provisions of Ordinance No. 5693 of said city, approved December 6, 1899."
